{"tid":2516750,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"hunter問題，古拿比加第一次捉到團長既時侯，團長突然宣佈旅團改名火箭兵團，會點？","createTime":"2021-05-05T00:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T01:59:26.000Z","uid":241151,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"598e97975357aa89fe5cfd2db184788e6909d492","tid":2516750,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"或者直接宣佈解散旅團，古拿比加會唔會即刻俾團長收皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你條鎖鏈只係用黎剋制到旅團，人地一解散同改名，旅團就唔存在，你吹佢漲呀？岩岩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819e67285029626e5535897bb4d8e5365a7adb92","tid":2516750,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"即場解決咗你條女人型再宣佈幻影旅團復出，你咬佢食呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8308717d9cea35af55aa82e6aa2dc746213a3944","tid":2516750,"uid":102716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:46:48.000Z","msg":"團長撚知佢能力"},{"pid":"3d8b940d01a378e7397117af93876fd70c771b9f","tid":2516750,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8308717d9cea35af55aa82e6aa2dc746213a3944","tid":2516750,"uid":102716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:46:48.000Z","msg":"團長撚知佢能力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"一開始咪講咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf979ad9fa82f3ba93a10ceca25c21f28fa61e9","tid":2516750,"uid":56957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:50:53.000Z","msg":"名呢樣嘢本來就毫無義意<br />\n唔通你叫自已做靚仔就真係靚仔咩<br />\n如果其他人唔係咁諗 咁靚仔呢隻字只會對你有意思<br />\n就好似黑警就算無咁自稱過 黑警依然係黑警<br />\n<br />\n同樣地旅團點改名都好 係所有人嘅認知都係幻影旅團<br />\n首爾始終係漢城<br />\n點改都改唔到古勒比加對幻影旅團嘅認知"},{"pid":"8134c8657acd0bd29e9e94bafe5c88cb5f1dc9eb","tid":2516750,"uid":16055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:51:00.000Z","msg":"船上已經講制約有少少似自己昆自己<br />\